I realized at some point that all of the algorithms I was

00:01:08.450 --> 00:01:11.320
doing for like biotechnology and aerospace and all that good stuff

00:01:11.340 --> 00:01:14.010
was in this like new and upcoming field that they were calling

00:01:14.010 --> 00:01:16.450
data science and that those people get paid a lot more money

00:01:16.450 --> 00:01:17.410
than I was making.

